{{Infobox officeholder |name = G S Bajpai |image = G. S. Bajpai.jpg |alt = G S Bajpai |caption = |office = Registrar and Professor, [[National Law University, Delhi]] |profession = Academic }}
'''G.S. Bajpai''' is an Indian professor of law.
==Career== Bajpai is presently serving as Professor, Registrar, Professor at K.L. Arora Chair in Criminal Law and also as the Chairperson at the Centre for Criminology & Victimology at [[National Law University, Delhi]]. From 2007‚Äì2011 he was Professor & Chairperson at the Centre for Criminal Justice Administration, [[National Law Institute University]], Bhopal (MP). He also had positions at the [[Indian Institute of Public Administration]], (1989) Bureau of Police Research & Development, (1989‚Äì1995) Punjab Police Academy, Punjab and Department of Criminology & Forensic Science, University of Saugar, MP.<ref>http://www.forensic.to/webhome/drgsbajpai/</ref>
